            <p class="text-ink-700 dark:text-ink-300 text-sm">
              I've tried brews from over 20 countries — from Mumbai's street-side filter kaapi to Dublin's third-wave cafés.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Midnight Engineer -->
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-sky-50 dark:from-ink-800 dark:to-ink-700 shadow-soft hover:shadow-chapter transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-200 to-sky-400 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
