              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 dark:text-ink-100 mb-2">Open Source Ally</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 dark:text-ink-300 text-sm">
              I contribute to GitHub projects and believe in technology that's inclusive, accessible, and community-built.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Lifelong Learner -->
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-lavender-50 dark:from-ink-800 dark:to-ink-700 shadow-soft hover:shadow-chapter transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-lavender-200 to-lavender-400 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12,3L1,9L12,15L21,10.09V17H23V9M5,13.18V17.18L12,21L19,17.18V13.18L12,17L5,13.18Z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 dark:text-ink-100 mb-2">Lifelong Learner</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 dark:text-ink-300 text-sm">
              From DevOps to Python ML libraries, I complete at least one technical course every month.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Problem Solver -->
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-butter-50 dark:from-ink-800 dark:to-ink-700 shadow-soft hover:shadow-chapter transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-butter-200 to-butter-400 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
